cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this benchmark, please cite it as below."
title: KR-Housing-LongRAG-Bench
abstract: >-
  A copyright-safe Korean long-context benchmark for evaluating whether
  full-context LLMs can replace or complement RAG and table/tool pipelines over
  real housing announcements (입주자모집공고), public tabular data (MOLIT 실거래 /
  HUG 분양이력), and housing statutes. The public release contains QA labels,
  evidence locators, deterministic predicates, answerability labels, split and
  provider/region metadata, and long-context-bundle references — no raw source
  documents, no leaked answers, and no API keys.
type: dataset
version: v0.6
date-released: "2026-06-05"
license: CC-BY-4.0
repository-code: "https://github.com/comsa33/kr-housing-longrag-bench"
